| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-1057 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3fc94bb4-eea2-5b5c-98b1-9131e2827ab7"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
